# Auto build EXE (Windows)

When you change **`src/`**, **`ui/`**, or **`scripts/build-release.ps1`** on a Windows machine:

1. Prefer **`.\scripts\watch-build-release.ps1 -Once`** for a single self-contained build (see `docs/LOCAL_DEVELOPMENT.md` §10).
2. Do **not** commit `dist/` — it is gitignored.
3. Cloud/Linux agents cannot produce the WinForms exe; note that in the handoff and rely on CI **Build release EXE** or the user's local watch script.

Log: `dist\watch-build.log`.
